Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA KWANZA</s></f>"},{ID:2,Style:{Background:{Image:"Bible.jpg",Luminosity:-30}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Matendo ya Mitume 
5: 27b-32, 40b-41</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Matendo ya Mitume	</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Siku zile: Kuhani mkuu aliwahoji mitume akasema, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Kuwakataza  tumewakataza kabisa kufundisha tena kwa jina hili.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Lakini tazama, mmejaza Yerusalemu kwa mafundisho yenu, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mwataka kuileta damu ya mtu huyu juu yetu.\"</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Petro na mitume wakajibu, “ Sharti kumtii Mungu Kuliko wanadamu.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Mungu wa baba  zetu amemfufua Yesu mliyemtundika ninyi msalabani na kumwua.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Huyo Mungu amemtukuza akae kulia kwake, awe Bwana na Mwokozi, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ili awajalie Waisraeli kuongoka na kuondolewa dhambi.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Mashahidi wa mambo haya ni sisi na Roho Mtakatifu ambaye Mungu huwapa wote wenye kumtii.” </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakawapiga (mitume) [milume] viboko wakawakataza wasifundishe tena </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa jina la Yesu, wakawaacha waende zao. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Nao wakatoka barazani wakijaa furaha kwa sababu walijaliwa kuaibishwa  kwa ajili ya jina la Yesu.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA </s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>Zaburi 30:2 na 4, 5-6, 
11-12a na 13b (K. 2a)</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Nakutukuza, ee Bwana, kwa kuwa umeniokoa.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nakutukuza, ee Bwana, kwa kuwa umeniokoa,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wala hukuwafurahisha adui zangu juu yangu.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ee Bwana, umeiondoa nafsi yangu kuzimuni;</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>umeniokoa katika wale wanaoshuka shimoni. (K)</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Nakutukuza, ee Bwana, kwa kuwa umeniokoa.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwimbieni Bwana, enyi waaminifu wake;</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>shukuruni jina lake takatifu,
kwani </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hasira yake ni ya kitambo kidogo;</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wema wake wadumu maisha yote.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kilio chaweza kikawapo usiku, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lakini asubuhi huja furaha. (K)</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Nakutukuza, ee Bwana, kwa kuwa umeniokoa.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Usikie, ee Bwana, unihurumie:
ee Bwana, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>uwe msaada wangu.
Umegeuza kilio changu kuwa furaha;</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ee Bwana, Mungu wangu, nitakushukuru milele. (K)</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Nakutukuza, ee Bwana, kwa kuwa umeniokoa.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI
Ufunuo 5:11-14</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Ufunuo wa Mtakatitu Yohane</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mimi, Yohane, niliona na kusikia sauti ya malaika wengi katika </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mzunguko wa kiti cha enzi na wa wenye uhai na wazee.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Hesabu yao haikuwa na idadi.
Wakasema kwa sauti kubwa:</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> “Mwanakondoo aliyechinjwa astahili kupokea uwezo, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>utajiri na hekima, nguvu na heshima, utukufu na sifa.\"</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Nikawasikia viumbe wote walioko mbinguni na duniani, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>katika ardhi na baharini, na wote waliomo wakisema:</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Mwenye kukaa katika kiti cha enzi na Mwanakondoo wanastahili sifa na </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>heshima,  utukufu na enzi daima na milele.\"</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hapo wenye uhai wanne wakasema: \"Amina.”</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na wazee wale wakaanguka kifudifudi, wakaabudu.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aleluya.          Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kristo amefufuka, yeye aliyeumba </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>vitu vyote na amewahurumia wanadamu wote.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aleluya.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Yohane</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule: 
Yesu alijionyesha tena kwa wafuasi </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wake kando ya Bahari ya Tiberia.
Alijionyesha hivi. </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Walikuwapo Simon Petro, na Tomaso aitwaye Pacha, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na Nathanaeli wa Kana ya Galilaya, na wana wa Zebedayo,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> na wengine wawili wa wafuasi wake. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Simoni Petro aliwaambia, 
\"Ninakwenda kuvua samaki.” </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nao wakamwambia, \"Nasi tutakwenda nawe.”</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi. wakatoka, wakapanda chombo, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lakini usiku ule hawakupata kitu. Asubuhi kulipopambazuka, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu alisimama ufukoni: lakini wafuasi </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hawakutambua kuwa ni Yesu. 
Yesu akawauliza,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> \"Wanangu, mna kitoweo?” Wakamjibu, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Hatuna.\" Basi akawaambia, 
\"Tupeni wavu upande </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa Kulia wa chombo, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
