Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa sababu ya wingi wa samaki. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hapo yule mfuasi ambaye Yesu alimpenda, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akamwambia Petro, 
