Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aliposikia ya kuwa ni Bwana, 
akajifunga vazi lake, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maana alikuwa bila nguo, akajitumbukiza baharini. </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wafuasi wengine wakafuata katika chombo </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wakivuta wavu uliojaa samaki, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa maana hawakuwa mbali na nchi kavu, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yaani yapata mitamia mbili tu.
Waliposhuka pwani, waliona moto </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa makaa na samaki juu yake, 
pia mkate. Yesu akawaambia, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Leteni baadhi ya samaki mliowavua sasa hivi.”</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi, Simoni Petro akapanda chomboni, akavuta wavu ufukoni,</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> uliojaa samaki wakubwa mia na hamsini na watatu. </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hata wavu haukupasuka kwa uzito wao. Yesu akawaambia, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Njoni mle chakula.\"Hakuna hata mmoja wa wafuasi aliyethubutu </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kumwuliza, \"Wewe u nani?” maana walijua ya kuwa ni Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Yesu akaja, akatwaa mkate akawapa, na samaki kadhalika.</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Safari hii ilikuwa ya tatu ya kujionyesha Yesu kwa wafuasi </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wake tangu kufufuka katika wafu.
Walipokwisha kula, </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu alimwuliza Simoni Petro, 
“Simoni, mwana wa Yohane,  </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wanipenda kuliko hawa?”
Akamjibu,</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> \"Ndiyo, Bwana, wajua ya kuwa nakupenda.”
 </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu akamwambia, \"Tunza wanakondoo wangu.”
Akamwuliza mara ya pili,</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>“Simoni, mwana wa Yohane, wanipenda?”  Naye akamjibu.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Ndiyo, Bwana, wajua ya kuwa nakupenda.” </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu akamwambia, \"Chunga kondoo wangu.” 
Akamwuliza mara ya tatu,</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Simoni, mwana wa Yohane, wanipenda?</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hapo Petro akahuzunika, kwa sababu alimwuliza mara ya tatu, \"Wanipenda?”</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na akamwambia, \"Bwana, unajua yote; unajua ya kuwa nakupenda.” </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu akamwambia, \"Tunza kondoo wangu. Amin, amin,</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> nakuambia, ulipokuwa kijana, ulijifunga kiuno mwenyewe, </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ukaenda ulikotaka; Lakini katika uzee, </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>utanyosha mikono yako, na mwingine atakufunga kiuno na kukupeleka usikotaka.”</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Kwa maneno hayo alimdokezea aina ya mauti atakayomtukuza nayo </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mungu. Baada ya kusema hayo, akamwambia, \"Nifuate.\"</s></f>"},{ID:28,
