Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akaona utukufu wa Mungu na Yesu amesimama kuume kwa Mungu,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akawaambia, \"Tazameni, ninaziona mbingu zimefunguka, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na
Mwana wa Mtu amesimama kuume kwa Mungu.\"</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nao wakapiga makelele sana, wakajiziba masikio, wakamshambulia
kwa nia moja. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakamtoa nje ya mji, wakampiga mawe. </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mashahidi
wakaweka nguo zao miguuni pa kijana mmoja, jina lake Sauli.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi, walipokuwa wakimtupia mawe Stefano, naye akasali na kuita,</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Bwana Yesu, ipokee roho yangu.\" </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akapiga magoti, akalia kwa
sauti kubwa, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Bwana, usiwahesabie dhambi hii.\"
Baada ya maneno hayo akazimia roho.
Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
Zaburi 97:1 )</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana ametamalaki, Aliye Juu, juu sana kuliko nchi yote.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana ametamalaki; nchi na ishangilie;
visiwa vingi na vifurahi.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hukumu na haki ni msingi wa kiti chake. </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana ametamalaki, Aliye Juu, juu sana kuliko nchi yote.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mbingu zinatangaza haki ya Mungu;
na mataifa yote wameuona utukufu wake.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Enyi, miungu wote mwangukieni yeye. K.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Bwana ametamalaki, Aliye Juu, juu sana kuliko nchi yote.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maana wewe ndiwe Bwana,
Uliye Juu juu, sana kuliko nchi yote,</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>umetukuka sana juu ya miungu yote. K.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Bwana ametamalaki, Aliye Juu, juu sana kuliko nchi yote.</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ufunuo 
22:12-14, 16-17, 20</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Ufunuo wa Mtakatifu Yohane</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mimi. Yohane, nilisikia sauti, ikaniambia,
\"Angalia, kuja kwangu ni karibu,</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na tuzo yangu i pamoja nami.
Nitamlipa kila mmoja kadiri ya matendo yake.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mimi ni Alfa na Omega,
ni wa kwanza na wa mwisho, ni mwanzo na kikomo.\"</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wenye heri wanaoosha mavazi yao.
Wataushiriki mti wa uzima,</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wapate kuingia mjini kwa kupita milangoni.
Mimi Yesu nimemtuma malaika wangu</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>awahakikishieni haya yahusuyo Makanisa.
Mimi ni mzizi na mzao wa Daudi</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tena nyota ya asubuhi inayong'aa.
Roho na bibi harusi wasema, \"Njoo.\"</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwenye kusikia aitikie, \"Njoo.\"
Mwenye kiu aje, mwenye kutaka </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>apokee maji ya uzima bila malipo.
Mwenye kushuhudia mambo haya asema,</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Kuja kwangu ni karibu.\"
Amina, njoo, Bwana Yesu!</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
Yohane 14:18</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. Aleluya.
W Aleluya,</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Sitawaacha ninyi kama yatima,
asema Bwana;</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nitakuja kwenu, na mioyo yenu itafurahi.</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI
Yohane 17:20-26</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Yohane</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule:</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>[Yesu aliinua macho yake kuelckea mbinguni akasali, akisema,
Baba Mtakatifu,]</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Si hao tu ninaowaombea,
lakini nawaombea pia wale watakaonisadiki kwa neno lao,</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ili wote wawe kitu kimoja, kama wewe Baba ulivyo ndani yangu,</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nami ndani yako, hao nao wawe ndani yetu,
hivyo ulimwengu upate kusadiki</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ya kuwa wewe ndiwe uliyenituma.
Nami nimewapa utukufu ule ulionipa mimi,</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ili wawe umoja kama sisi tulivyo umoja,
Mimi ndani yao, nawe ndani yangu,</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ili wawe kamili katika umoja,</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ulimwengu utambue ya kuwa ni wewe uliyenituma,</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na umewapenda hao kama ulivyonipenda mimi.</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Baba, nataka hao ulionipa wawe nami pale nilipo mimi,</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ili waone utukufu ulionipa,</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa kuwa umenipenda tangu kuumbwa kwa ulimwengu.</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Baba mwadilifu,
ulimwengu haukukutambua, </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lakini mimi nimekutambua,
na hao wametambua ya kuwa ni wewe uliyenituma.</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nimewatambulisha jina lako, 
na nitaendelea kulitambulisha,</s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ili upendo ulionipendea mimi uwe ndani yao,
nami niwe ndani yao.\"</s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"DOMINIKA YA SABA YA PASAKA MWAKA C"},{Guid:"T2Fgvfeii0OcsWnTkn0aDA",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA MBERE
Atumwo 10: 34, 37-43.</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŪTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA ATUMWO:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mithenya-inĩ io, Peter-agïitīka kwaria akiuga atīrī: Inyuĩ nĩ mũũi, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naguo nīguo wahunjanĩirio Judea guothe wambïrïirio o Galilea, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>thutha wa rīrĩa John aaheanire ũhoro wa atî andű mabatithio. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Naguo ni wa Yesu wa Nazareth, űrĩa Ngai aaműitīrīirie Muoyo Mütheru o na hinya; </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nake agicanga agīīkaga maūndūmega, na akîhonagia andű arĩa </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>othe maatüire manyariragwo nĩ műcukani: nĩ gűkoruo Ngai aarī hamwe nake. </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na ithuĩ- rĩ, tūrī aira a maũndű macio mothe ekire küu bürüri wa Ayahudi, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na Jerusalemu. Nake nĩ oragiruo nĩ andű na kűműcuuria műtī igūrũ. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nīwe Ngai aariűkirie műthenya wa gatatű, agīītīkīra atī acoke kuoneka, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no ti kuonwo nĩ andű othe, tiga o aira arĩa maathurirão o mbere nĩ Ngai, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nao não ithuĩ, o ithuĩ arĩa twarïaga na tűkanyuaga hamwe na-ke, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aarīkia kūriūka akoima kūrī arĩa akuũ. </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na gūtwatha nĩ aatwathire ati tűhunjagīrie andű, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na tuumbūrage atĩ we niwe watuiruo nĩ Ngai Műtui-cira wa </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>andū arĩa marĩ muoyo na wa arĩa makuĩ-te. </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nao irori ciothe niwe maheanagīra ũira, makoimbūra atĩ nĩ ũndű </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa rīītwa rĩake mündű o wothe ürĩa </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũgakorão amwīhoketę nĩ akoherão mehia make.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nício ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GŪCOKERUO</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Thaburi 118: 1-2; 16-17; 22-23.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA :Müthenya ũyũ nĩ Mwathani ütümīte ügïe, Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>I gīcokeriei Mwathani ngatho, tondu ni mwega; </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tondū ūtugi wake ni wa tene na tene.</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>A Israeli ta ni moige üguo, atī ūtugi wake nĩ wa tene na tene.</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA :Müthenya ũyũ nĩ Mwathani ütümīte ügïe, Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Guoko kwa ūrio kwa Mwathani nî gwītüügīrīire; </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>guoko kwa ūrio kwa Mwathani gwīkaga o
maūndū ma ūhoti! </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Niī gūkua-rī, ndigūkua, nî gūtūūra ngūtūūra muoyo, </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nganage mawīko ma
Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA :Müthenya ũyũ nĩ Mwathani ütümīte ügïe, Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ihiga rīrīa rīaregirão nī aaki nīrio rītuīkīte o rīrīa inene ria koine.</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ündū ūcio uumīte kwĩ Mwathani, na ni ügütügegia tūkīwona.</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA :Müthenya ũyũ nĩ Mwathani ütümīte ügïe, Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA IGĪRĪ
Akolosai 3: 1-4.</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA MA MARUA MUTHURE PAUL KŪRĪ ANDU A KOLOSAI :</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariŭ a Ithe witű, hakīrī ūguo-rĩ, mũngīkoruo nĩ mwariűkirio hamwe </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na Kristű no kīmathagei maũndũ marĩa marī Igűrű, kūrĩa Kristű arī, </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aikaire guoko-inĩ kwa ũrĩo kwa Ngai. Rūmbūyagiai maũndű </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>marĩa marī Igűrű, na mütigage kűrűmbūyia marĩa marĩ thĩ. </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ ũndũ nĩ mwakwire, naguo muoyo wanyu nĩ mühithe hamwe na </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kristũ thinĩ wa Ngai. Na rīrĩa Kristű, o we űrĩ muoyo witű, akonanio,</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hindĩ ĩo o na inyuĩ ni mũkonanio hamwe nake mwĩ na riri.</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nīcio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kana:
1 Akorintho 5:6-8.</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŪTHOMA MARUA MA MUTHURE PAUL KURI ANDU A KORINTHO :</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariũ a Ithe witű, kai műtoï atī gacunji kanini ka ndawa ya kűimbia </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>műgate nĩ kaimbagia kimere
kĩu giothe ? Tei ndawa io ya tene, </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>îthire biũ, nĩ getha műtuïke kīmere kĩa műkiyano, </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>műtakīrī ekîre ndawa ĩo. Nĩ gűkoruo Paska iitű nï ïrīkītie </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>güthinjwo ya igongona, nayo niyo Kristů. Tondű ūcio-rĩ, nĩ tűkīrīage giathĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hatari na ndawa ïo ya tene ya kűimbia műgate, </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>io ningĩ ya üüru na ya waganu; no nĩ tūkīrīage kīrī na műgate ürĩa űtarī mũimbie, </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũguo nĩ kuuga tükïrïage tütarī na ühinga,
na tūrī na ũhoro-ürĩa-wa-ma.</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nício ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RŪĪMBO RUA ALLELUYA
1 Akorintho 5: 7-8.</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya, Alleluya. </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu Paska iitű nĩ athīnjitwo.</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Rekei tũgĩe na thigũkũũ thĩinĩ wa Mwathani. </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA INJIRI
John 20:1-9.</s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŪTHOMA INJIRI YA MUTHURE JOHN :</s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Müthenya wa kwambīrīria kiumia Maria Magdalena akīroka </s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mbīrīra-inī rūcinī tene, kūrī o nduma, akiona ihiga rii ithengie muungu-inī. </s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Agīgīteng'era, agīthiĩ gwĩ Simone Petro, na kwĩ műrutwo ürĩa ũngĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>űrĩa Yesu endete, akīmera atīrī: Nĩ marutīte Mwathani muungu-inĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na tūtiũi hara mamũigīte. Petro agīkiumagara o na mūrutwo ũcio ũngĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>magĩthii marorete mbîrîra-inĩ. Makīgwata gūteng'era o</s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>erī, nake mūrutwo ücio ũngĩ agīkīria Petro ihenya, </s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agīkinya muungu-inĩ mbere; na aainamīrīra aarora thĩini, </s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akiona matama marĩa ma gatani me maige thĩ, na ndatonye. </s></f>"},{ID:74,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Simone Petro nake agīgīūka, a-
mūrūmīrīire, </s></f>"},{ID:75,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agītonya muungu thììnĩ; nake akiona matama macio ma gatani me </s></f>"},{ID:76,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maige thĩ, o na gĩtambaya nakĩo kīrĩa kĩarī mūtwe wake, </s></f>"},{ID:77,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gītaigītwo hamwe na matama macio ma gatani, nĩ gũkūnjwo giakūnjītwo </s></f>"},{ID:78,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gīkaigwo handū mwanya. </s></f>"},{ID:79,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hindĩ ĩo mũrutwo ũcio ũngĩ nake agīgītonya, ūcio waambire </s></f>"},{ID:80,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gūkinya muungu-inī, nake akïona, agīītīkia. Amu nginya hĩndĩ ĩo </s></f>"},{ID:81,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>matiamenyete wega ühoro ürĩa wandikītwo, atĩ no műhaka acoke </s></f>"},{ID:82,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ariűke oime kwi arĩa akuũ.</s></f>"},{ID:83,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nicio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"KIUMIA KĨA IRIŪKIRO - PASAKA
 MWAKA C"},{Guid:"Uw1LyUZ+EkmU59zUeZ1g4Q",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA KWANZA
Matendo ya Mitume 5:12-16</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Matendo ya Mitume</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa mikono ya mitume zikafanyika ishara </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na miujiza mingi kati ya watu. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na wote walikutana kwa nia moja katika Ukumbi
wa Sulemani. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Miongoni mwa wengine hakuthubutu mtu kujiunga
nao, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lakini wote waliwasifu.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Umati wa wanaume na wanawake wenye </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kumwamini Bwana uliongezeka zaidi na zaidi. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakapeleka hata wagonjwa barabarani, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wakawalaza juu ya vitanda na magodoro ili Petro </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akipita walau kila mmoja wao atiwe kivuli chake. </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Pia watu wengi wa miji ya jirani ya Yerusalemu </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>walikutana wakileta wagonjwa na</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wenye kusumbuliwa na pepo wachafu, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nao wote wakaponywa.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
Zaburi 118:2-4, 22-24, 25-27a </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Mshukuruni Bwana kwa kuwa ni mwema,</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa maana wema wake ni wa milele.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Israeli na aseme sasa:
wema wake ni wa milele.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nyumba ya Haruni iseme:
wema wake ni wa milele.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wamchao Bwana waseme:
wema wake ni wa milele.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Mshukuruni Bwana kwa kuwa ni mwema,</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa maana wema wake ni wa milele.</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Jiwe walilolikataa waashi
limekuwa jiwe kuu la pembeni.</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Jambo hili alilifanya Bwana;
nalo ni la ajabu machoni petu.</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hii ndiyo siku aliyoifanya Bwana;
tuishangilie na kuifurahia. </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Mshukuruni Bwana kwa kuwa ni mwema,</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa maana wema wake ni wa milele.</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ee Bwana, tunakusihi, utuokoe!</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ee Bwana, tunakusihi, utufanikishe!</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mbarikiwa yeye ajaye kwa jina la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tunawabariki ninyi toka nyumba ya Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana ni Mungu, naye ametuangazia. </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Mshukuruni Bwana kwa kuwa ni mwema,</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa maana wema wake ni wa milele.</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI
Ufunuo 1:9-11a, 12-13, 17-19</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Nalikuwa nimekufa, </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lakini kumbe niko hai daima na milele.\"</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Ufunuo wa Mtakatifu Yohane
Mimi, Yohane, </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndugu yenu na mwenzenu katika masumbufu</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ufalme na uvumilivu pamoja na Yesu, </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nalikuwako kwenye kisiwa cha Patmosi </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa ajili ya neno la Mungu na kumshuhudia
Yesu. </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Siku ya Bwana nilishikwa na Roho, </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nikasikia nyuma yangu
sauti kubwa kama ya tarumbeta. </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ikasema, \"Unayoona uyaandike
katika kitabu, </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ukakipeleke kwa Makanisa saba.\"</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nikageuka nione ilikuwa sauti ya nani iliyosema nami. </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Baada ya kugeuka, </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>niliona vinara saba vya mishumaa vya dhahabu.</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na katikati ya vinara vya mishumaa, </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nilimwona mwenye kuonekana kama Mwana wa mtu, </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>amevaa kanzu ndefu mpaka</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwenye visigino na ukanda wa dhahabu kifuani pake.</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nilipomwona nilianguka miguuni pake kama mtu aliyekufa.</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kumbe yeye akaweka mkono wake wa kulia juu yangu.</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akasema: \"Usiogope! Mimi ni wa kwanza na wa mwisho, </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na yeye aliye hai. Nalikuwa nimekufa, </s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lakini kumbe niko hai daima na milele. </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nami ninazo funguo za mauti na za kuzimu. </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Sasa andika uliyoyaona: </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yaliyopo na yatakayokuwako baadaye.\"</s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
Yohane 20:29</s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Aleluya. W. Aleluya. </s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa kuwa umeniona, Tomaso, umesadiki,
asema Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wenye heri wale wasioona na wakasadiki.</s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI
Yohane 20:19-31</s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Yohane</s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Jioni ya siku ile ya kwanza ya juma,</s></f>"},{ID:74,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>alikuja Yesu, akasimama katikati,</s></f>"},{ID:75,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ingawa milango ya chumba walimokaa wafuasi </s></f>"},{ID:76,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ilikuwa imefungwa
kwa kuwaogopa Wayahudi, </s></f>"},{ID:77,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akawaambia,
\"Amani iwe nanyi.\"</s></f>"},{ID:78,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Baada ya maneno hayo,</s></f>"},{ID:79,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akawaonyesha mikono yake na ubavu wake.</s></f>"},{ID:80,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wafuasi wakafurahi walipomwona Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:81,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu akawaambia mara ya pili,
\"Amani iwe nanyi.</s></f>"},{ID:82,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kama Baba alivyonituma mimi,
nami nawatuma ninyi.\"</s></f>"},{ID:83,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Baada ya maneno hayo,
akawapulizia, akawaambia,</s></f>"},{ID:84,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Pokeeni Roho Mtakatifu.</s></f>"},{ID:85,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wowote mtakaowaondolea dhambi, </s></f>"},{ID:86,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wameondolewa,
wowote mtakaowafungia dhambi,</s></f>"},{ID:87,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wamefungiwa.\"</s></f>"},{ID:88,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Lakini Tomaso, aitwaye Pacha,</s></f>"},{ID:89,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mmoja wa wale Kumi na Wawili.</s></f>"},{ID:90,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hakuwako pamoja nao alipokuja Yesu.</s></f>"},{ID:91,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi, wafuasi wengine wakamwambia,</s></f>"},{ID:92,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Tumemwona Bwana.\"</s></f>"},{ID:93,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yeye lakini akawajibu,</s></f>"},{ID:94,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Nisipoona matundu ya misumari mikononi mwake,</s></f>"},{ID:95,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kutia kidole changu sehemu za misumari,</s></f>"},{ID:96,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kutia mkono wangu katika ubavu wake,</s></f>"},{ID:97,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>sisadiki hata kidogo.\"</s></f>"},{ID:98,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Baada ya siku nane,</s></f>"},{ID:99,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wafuasi wake walikuwamo tena chumbani,</s></f>"},{ID:100,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na Tomaso pamoja nao.</s></f>"},{ID:101,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akaja Yesu, ingawa milango ilikuwa imefungwa,</s></f>"},{ID:102,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akasimama katikati, akasema,
\"Amani iwe nanyi.\"</s></f>"},{ID:103,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kisha akamwambia Tomaso,</s></f>"},{ID:104,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Tia kidole chako humu, tazama mikono yangu,</s></f>"},{ID:105,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lete mkono wako na kuutia katika ubavu wangu</s></f>"},{ID:106,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na usikose imani, bali uwe mwamini.\"</s></f>"},{ID:107,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tomaso akajibu akamwambia,</s></f>"},{ID:108,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Bwana wangu na Mungu wangu!\"</s></f>"},{ID:109,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu akamwambia, \"Kwa kuwa umeniona, </s></f>"},{ID:110,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>umesadiki?</s></f>"},{ID:111,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wenye heri wale wasioona, wakasadiki.\"</s></f>"},{ID:112,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Sasa Yesu alifanya ishara nyingine nyingi mbele ya wafuasi wake</s></f>"},{ID:113,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>zisizoandikwa katika kitabu hiki.</s></f>"},{ID:114,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Lakini hizi zimeandikwa, mpate kusadiki</s></f>"},{ID:115,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ya kuwa Yesu ni Masiya, Mwana wa Mungu,</s></f>"},{ID:116,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tena kwa kusadiki mpate kuwa na uzima kwa jina lake.</s></f>"},{ID:117,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,Style:{Footer:{Template:" "}},
Text:"DOMINIKA YA PILI YA PASAKA(au ya Huruma ya Mungu)MWAKA C"}],Guid:"kL5klYRjw0aHNhPqb+svLg",
Text:"DOMINIKA ZA PASAKA MWAKA C"}